    <stitle>STEERING COLUMN ASSEMBLY, TILT/TELESCOPING - MAINTENANCE - LUBRICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <para>The steering shaft slip joint and the universal joints should be lubricated at assembly and at the
            intervals indicated in the Operator's Manual of the vehicle being serviced. Lubricate with Fleetrite EP2
            Moly Grease or equivalent NLGI#2 multi-purpose lithium grease.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
